          RESET     DEFPATH
.
          PACK      DEFPATH,DEFPATH,SP30,SP30,SP30,SP30
          STRIP     DEFPATH
          ENDSET    DEFPATH
          RESET     DEFPATH
          CLOSE     FINDFILE
          MOVE      ZERO,EXIT
          GOTO      DEFT9999
.
